channel.title: Comments on: Friday Go Forward: Week 17

item.title: By: Ben
item.dc:creator: Ben
item.description: The Lessons Learned was a section that came from personal experience. So it could be that I acquired them while solving a problem, reading a book, playing a game, or getting a game review from a stronger player. But they are more like "Aha!" moments as opposed to just new things I learned.
